Sprint gets $ 8 . 1 million prison contract . Sprint Corp said Tuesday it won an $ 8 . 1 million contract from the state of Nebraska to provide long - distance telephone services for inmates at 11 state correctional facilities . The contract is for five years with two one - year options for renewal by the state , Sprint said . Sprint will provide the service in conjunction with Magnasync Corp and Smart Data Connections Inc . Under the contract , Sprint and its associates will install collect - call telephones , provide call monitoring and other security equipment , and provide staff members to operate elements of the service . ( ( - - Chicago newsdesk , 312 - 408 - 8787 ) ) 
